<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <title>One month's dry-waste</title>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.4.1/css/bootstrap.min.css">
  <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.6.0/jquery.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.4.1/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
  <style>
  .carousel-inner > .item > img,
  .carousel-inner > .item > a > img {
    width: 80%;
    margin: auto;
  }
  
  h1{
    color: black;
    font: initial;
    font-size: 50px;
  }
  h2{
    color: white;
    font: initial;
    font-size: 50px;
  }
  h3{
    color: black;
    font-size: 15px;
  }
  h4{
    color: white;
    font-size: 15px;
  }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container mt-3">
    <div class="d-flex flex-row-reverse">
      <br>
      <div>
        <a href="donorlogin.ejs"><button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Donor's Login</button></a>
        <a href="receiverlogin.ejs"><button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Receiver's Login</button></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="container mt-3">
    <h1>One month's dry-waste</h1>
    <p>A smart recycling system to resolve landfill problem</p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="container">
    <ul class="nav">
      <li class="nav-item">
        <a class="nav-link" href="/about">About</a>
      </li>
      <li class="nav-item">
        <a class="nav-link" href="/recyclableItems">Recyclable items</a>
      </li>
      <li class="nav-item">
        <a class="nav-link" href="/stepstofollow">Steps to follow</a>
      </li>
      <li class="nav-item">
        <a class="nav-link" href="/privacy">Privacy</a>
      </li>
      <li class="nav-item">
        <a class="nav-link" href="/faq">FAQs</a>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>  

<div class="container">
  <br>
  <div id="myCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
    <ol class="carousel-indicators">
      <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
      <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="1"></li>
      <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="2"></li>
      <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="3"></li>
      <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="4"></li>
    </ol>

    <div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox">

      <div class="item active">
        <img src="../images/welcome.webp" width="460" height="350">
        <div class="carousel-caption">
          <h1>Welcome</h1>
          <h3>Let's have a smart recycling process so that dry waste gets recycled before going to landfill</h3>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="item">
        <img src="../images/landfill.jpg" width="460" height="350">
        <div class="carousel-caption">
          <h2>Landfill</h2>
          <h4>The size of landfill is getting increased day by day. Wet-waste and day-waste both are dumped together to the landfill. Very less amount of dry-waste are recycled from here</h4>
        </div>
      </div>
    
      <div class="item">
        <img src="../images/segregate.webp" width="460" height="350">
        <div class="carousel-caption">
          <h2>Segregate</h2>
          <h4>We can segregate wet-waste and dry-waste. We can store the dry-waste for a month at our home and we can deliver it directly to the recycling industry</h4>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="item">
        <img src="../images/donor.jpeg" width="460" height="350">
        <div class="carousel-caption">
          <h1>Donor</h1>
          <h3>We all individuals can store dry-waste for a month at home and we can book a request using "Donor's Login" to be picked all the dry-waste from our home or we can drop the dry-waste to the nearest recycling industry</h3>
        </div>
      </div>

      
      <div class="item">
        <img src="../images/receiver.jpg" width="460" height="350">
        <div class="carousel-caption">
          <h2>Receiver</h2>
          <h4>Person who are working with recycling industry can login using "Receiver's Login" to check the requests by the Donor and can come to Donor's home to collect all the dry-waste</h4>
        </div>
      </div>
  
    </div>

    <!-- Left and right controls -->
    <a class="left carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
      <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
    </a>
    <a class="right carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
      <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>